Below is a comprehensive HTML, CSS, and JavaScript code for a fictional "Selling Planets" store. This store sells various types of software, applications, and tech-related products.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Selling Planets - The Next Evolution in Software</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            color: #fff;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .store-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 0;
            background-color: #0a0a0a;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 3em;
            color: #00ffff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px #00ffff;
        }

        .product-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .product-card {
            background-color: #333;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 15px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .product-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .product-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .product-info {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .product-title {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #00ffff;
        }

        .product-price {
            color: #ff00ff;
            font-size: 1.3em;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        .buy-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #00ffff;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .buy-button:hover {
            background-color: #00ffff;
        }

        .cart-icon {
            position: fixed;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            color: #00ffff;
            font-size: 24px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .opened-modal {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
        }

        .closed-modal {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 200px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .product-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="store-container">
        <header>
            <div class="logo">Selling Planets</div>
            <p>Where Innovation Meets Imagination</p>
        </header>

        <div class="product-grid">
            <!-- Application Software -->
            <div class="product-card">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200x200" alt="App Software" class="product-image">
                <div class="product-info">
                    <div class="product-title">CosmicOS</div>
                    <div class="product-price">$49.99</div>
                    <button class="buy-button">Buy Now</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Games -->
            <div class="product-card">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200x200" alt="Games" class="product-image">
                <div class="product-info">
                    <div class="product-title">Galaxy Gamelord</div>
                    <div class="product-price">$59.99</div>
                    <button class="buy-button">Buy Now</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Security -->
            <div class="product-card">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200x200" alt="Security" class="product-image">
                <div class="product-info">
                    <div class="product-title">NeuralNetShield</div>
                    <div class="product-price">$99.99</div>
                    <button class="buy-button">Buy Now</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Development Tools -->
            <div class="product-card">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200x200" alt="Tools" class="product-image">
                <div class="product-info">
                    <div class="product-title">CodeCraft</div>
                    <div class="product-price">$149.99</div>
                    <button class="buy-button">Buy Now</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Space Exploration -->
            <div class="product-card">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200x200" alt="Exploration" class="product-image">
                <div class="product-info">
                    <div class="product-title">StarMap Pro</div>
                    <div class="product-price">$199.99</div>
                    <button class="buy-button">Buy Now</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- AI Solutions -->
            <div class="product-card">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200x200" alt="AI" class="product-image">
                <div class="product-info">
                    <div class="product-title">MindCore</div>
                    <div class="product-price">$299.99</div>
                    <button class="buy-button">Buy Now</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cart-icon" onclick="toggleModal()">🛒</div>

    <!-- Modal -->
    <div id="modal" class="opened-modal">
        <div class="closed-modal">
            <h2>Your Cart</h2>
            <p>Nothing in your cart yet!</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function toggleModal() {
            const modal = document.getElementById('modal');
            if (modal.classList.contains('opened-modal')) {
                modal.classList.remove('opened-modal');
                modal.classList.add('closed-modal');
            } else {
                modal.classList.add('opened-modal');
            }
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
```

This code creates a futuristic tech store interface with the following features:

1. A header with the store logo and tagline
2. Responsive product grid layout that adjusts based on screen size
3. Product cards with:
   - Image placeholder (you can replace with actual images)
   - Title
   - Price
   - Buy Now button
4. Floating cart icon
5. Modal for displaying cart contents

The design uses a dark theme with cyan (#00ffff) as the accent color, creating a futuristic and space-like aesthetic.

To use this code:

1. Replace all placeholder images (via.placeholder.com) with actual product images.
2. Adjust prices and product descriptions as needed.
3. Add additional products by copying and modifying the existing product cards in the HTML.

The CSS includes:
- Responsive grid layout
- Hover effects on product cards
- Smooth transitions
- Mobile-friendly design
- Modern color scheme

You can further customize this code by:
- Adding more animations
- Implementing a proper cart system with local storage or backend integration
- Adding user authentication
- Including more interactive features
